data.description: A gorgeous and spacious 1 BR, 1 BA condo w/ garage parking space included in Town Square Tower, in the heart of SW Waterfront and all it's great attractions.. This wonderful pet friendly MCM building has it all: stunning lobby, fitness room, wonderful outdoor pool, convenient laundry on every floor, 24 hour full service front desk, on-site management, and the condo fee includes all utilities! This unit boasts beautiful inlaid hardwood floors, large concrete balcony adding outdoor space w/ privacy and viewing the street and park from the front of the building. Enjoy plenty of closet space. The awesome kitchen has modern natural wood shaker style cabinets, granite tops and stainless steel. The bathroom offers a large step in shower tastefully done with attractive subway tile. The unit feels spacious w/ room for all that you do at home.. This attractive unit w/ custom finishes throughout is ready for a new owner w/ no projects needed. Come and enjoy.
